title: The Tea Party- 41 Live Shows and Indie
description:
The Tea Party- 38 lives shows and rare Indie album. I was a teenager in Buffalo, NY in the late 90s and loved The Tea Party. I even got to see them live a few times. In the late 90s and early 00's there was a ftp site that hosted many of these, but has long since gone down. Due to the unavailability of many of these shows, I have decided to make them available once again. This is my first torrent ever. Please seed to keep this going.
